"},{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","abstract":[{"text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/pickerStyle(_:)":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"pickerStyle","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"S","kind":"genericParameter"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"text":"S","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP"}],"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"pickerStyle(_:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/pickerStyle(_:)","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip\/pickerstyle(_:)","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}